```plantuml
@startuml eProsima_Integration-Service

actor Client
participant "JSON Library" as JSON
participant "Integration Service" as IS
participant "System Handle" as SH

Client -> IS: Send Request
activate IS

IS -> JSON: Parse JSON (from Client)
activate JSON
JSON -> JSON: Lexical Analysis
JSON -> JSON: Syntax Analysis
JSON -> IS: Return Parsed Data
deactivate JSON

IS -> SH: Route Message
activate SH

SH -> SH: Convert Data
SH -> SH: Communicate with Middleware
SH -> IS: Return Response
deactivate SH

IS -> JSON: Serialize Response
activate JSON
JSON -> JSON: Serialization
JSON -> IS: Return Serialized JSON
deactivate JSON

IS -> Client: Send Response
deactivate IS

@enduml
```